follow the item chromium on wiki.archlinux.org
you can install chromim-pepper-flash from aur
now because the package use some packages on dl.google.com in PKGBUILD
so download the files it needs, and store them in the folder which include PKGBUILD
and then run makepkg -s to make *.pkg.tar.gz, and then run sudo pacman -U *.pkg.tar.gz to install